      <title>《班扎古鲁白玛的沉默》</title>
      <link>http://:1313/tmp/2011/01/%E7%8F%AD%E6%89%8E%E5%8F%A4%E9%B2%81%E7%99%BD%E7%8E%9B%E7%9A%84%E6%B2%89%E9%BB%98/</link>
